on - Search.png\" data-image-key=\"Icon_-_Search.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ef/Icon_-_Search.png/revision/latest?cb=20120427204701\" /></a></span></span></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"scale\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Scale</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><ul><li>1/144 <span class=\"plainlinks\" title=\"Search the other 6 pages containing the property &quot;Scale&quot; with the value &quot;1/144&quot;\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://gundam.fandom.com/wiki/Special:SearchByProperty?property=Scale&amp;value=1%2F144\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"Icon - Search\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Icon - Search.png\" data-image-key=\"Icon_-_Search.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ef/Icon_-_Search.png/revision/latest?cb=20120427204701\" /></a></span></span></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"era\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Era</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/After_Colony\" title=\"After Colony\">After Colony</a> <span class=\"plainlinks\" title=\"Search the other 254 pages containing the property &quot;Era&quot; with the value &quot;After Colony&quot;\"><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"https://gundam.fandom.com/wiki/Special:SearchByProperty?property=Era&amp;value=After+Colony\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"Icon - Search\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"12\" height=\"12\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Icon - Search.png\" data-image-key=\"Icon_-_Search.png\" data-relevant=\"0\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/e/ef/Icon_-_Search.png/revision/latest?cb=20120427204701\" /></a></span></span></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</aside>\n\n</p><p><b>High Grade After Colony (HGAC)</b> is a line of 1/144 scale <a href=\"/wiki/Gunpla\" title=\"Gunpla\">Gunpla</a> model kits of the <a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suits\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Mobile Suits\">Mobile Suits</a> from the <a href=\"/wiki/After_Colony\" title=\"After Colony\">After Colony</a> timeline of the <i>Gundam</i> meta series. First produced in 2013, the line is a spin-off of the <a href=\"/wiki/High_Grade_Universal_Century\" title=\"High Grade Universal Century\">High Grade Universal Century</a> line, with it's releases being numbered as such.\n</p><p>To prepare for the 40th anniversary of Gunpla in 2020, the \"Gunpla Evolution Project\" began in 2017. Showcasing improvements and innovations in specific areas, this project involved Gunpla from multiple lines, with one of them being a kit of the <a href=\"/wiki/OZ-06MS_Leo\" title=\"OZ-06MS Leo\">OZ-06MS Leo</a>.\n</p><p>Following the reorganization of Bandai Namco Group, box covers of reissue and future release of kits from September 2018 onwards feature a blue Bandai logo instead of the original red logo, while releases and reissues from mid-2022 onwards further feature the Bandai Namco logo on the upper right corner.\n</p><p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Regulars_and_Special_Editions\">Regulars and Special Editions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fgundam.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FHigh_Grade_After_Colony%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"fandom-table\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>HGAC #\n</th>\n<th>Model\n</th>\n<th>Series\n</th>\n<th>Yen Price\n</th>\n<th>Release Date\n</th>\n<th>Notes\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>162\n<p><span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/130px-HGUC-Gundam-Wing-Box_Art.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20200514023447\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"130px-HGUC-Gundam-Wing-Box Art\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"180\" height=\"114\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"130px-HGUC-Gundam-Wing-Box Art.jpg\" data-image-key=\"130px-HGUC-Gundam-Wing-Box_Art.jpg\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/4/4c/130px-HGUC-Gundam-Wing-Box_Art.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/180?cb=20200514023447\" /></a></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/XXXG-01W_Wing_Gundam\" title=\"XXXG-01W Wing Gundam\">XXXG-01W Wing Gundam</a>\n</td>\n<td><i><a href=\"/wiki/Mobile_Suit_Gundam_Wing\" title=\"Mobile Suit Gundam Wing\">Mobile Suit Gundam Wing</a></i>\n</td>\n<td>\u00a51,500\n</td>\n<td>2013 September\n</td>\n<td>First HGAC kit released. Fully transformable kit.\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>174<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File/Frameless\"><a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/gundam/images/0/00/HG_Wing_Zero_Boxart.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20140227060735\" class=\"mw-file-description image\"><img alt=\"HG Wing Zero Bo